  ('social-worker-moex-05923', 'social-worker', 'social-worker-moex-105-f2e04173', 'sub-social-worker-05', NULL, 'single_choice', '不同利益關係人對方案評估有不同利益考量。一項完善的評估進行中，除了最被重視的兩項倫理「告知 同意」、「隱私與保密」之外，下列那一項方案倫理比較重要？', '["利害相關者的潛在風險", "投資的利益成果評估", "方案成果分配", "領導風格"]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:10:32+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "9e4d5d193ead", "answer_pdf_sha1": "c3d41c596c6d", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "105090", "c": "107", "s": "0603", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "乙、測驗題部分", "subject": "社會工作管理", "year": "105", "exam_name": "105年第二次中醫師分階段營養師心理師護理師社工師暨法醫師語言治療師聽力師牙體技術師考試", "original_question_number": 14, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "socialworker", "db_exam_id": "social-worker"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('social-worker-moex-05924', 'social-worker', 'social-worker-moex-105-f2e04173', 'sub-social-worker-05', NULL, 'single_choice', '在團體決策的方法中，較能兼顧聚集討論及獨立思考的方法是那一種？', '["腦力激盪法", "名義團體法", "得爾菲技術法", "電子會議"]'::jsonb, 1, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:10:32+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "9e4d5d193ead", "answer_pdf_sha1": "c3d41c596c6d", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "105090", "c": "107", "s": "0603", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "乙、測驗題部分", "subject": "社會工作管理", "year": "105", "exam_name": "105年第二次中醫師分階段營養師心理師護理師社工師暨法醫師語言治療師聽力師牙體技術師考試", "original_question_number": 15, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "socialworker", "db_exam_id": "social-worker"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('social-worker-moex-05925', 'social-worker', 'social-worker-moex-105-f2e04173', 'sub-social-worker-05', NULL, 'single_choice', '如果在某一社區推動方案，進行方案需求評估，最常用的便捷方法是「社區印象法（community impressions approach）」，下列那一個評估作法不屬之？', '["社區普查（census）", "社區會議（community forums）", "名義團體（nominal groups）", "訪問重要資訊提供者（key informants）"]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:10:32+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "9e4d5d193ead", "answer_pdf_sha1": "c3d41c596c6d", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "105090", "c": "107", "s": "0603", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "乙、測驗題部分", "subject": "社會工作管理", "year": "105", "exam_name": "105年第二次中醫師分階段營養師心理師護理師社工師暨法醫師語言治療師聽力師牙體技術師考試", "original_question_number": 16, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "socialworker", "db_exam_id": "social-worker"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('social-worker-moex-05926', 'social-worker', 'social-worker-moex-105-f2e04173', 'sub-social-worker-05', NULL, 'single_choice', '方案結束後，其所產生成效的延續性或造成的衝擊，予以進行評估（evaluation），叫做：', '["影響評估（impact evaluation）", "結果評估（evaluation of outcome）", "可行性評估（feasibility evaluation）", "成本效益評估（cost-effectiveness evaluation）"]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:10:32+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "9e4d5d193ead", "answer_pdf_sha1": "c3d41c596c6d", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "105090", "c": "107", "s": "0603", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "乙、測驗題部分", "subject": "社會工作管理", "year": "105", "exam_name": "105年第二次中醫師分階段營養師心理師護理師社工師暨法醫師語言治療師聽力師牙體技術師考試", "original_question_number": 17, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "socialworker", "db_exam_id": "social-worker"}'::jsonb, NULL),
