  ('social-worker-moex-05928', 'social-worker', 'social-worker-moex-105-f2e04173', 'sub-social-worker-05', NULL, 'single_choice', '預算管理是社會工作管理的重要項目，如果預算管理之編列是以上一年度各項目編列多少，視財源狀況 及物價指數或政策偏愛，予以提高或縮減，這種預算制度最簡便，也有利於傳承，但也容易造成一些浪 費。此一方法較適當的名稱叫做：', '["零基預算（zero-based budget）", "方案預算（program budget）", "功能預算（functional budget）", "遞增預算（incremental budget）"]'::jsonb, 3, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:10:32+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "9e4d5d193ead", "answer_pdf_sha1": "c3d41c596c6d", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "105090", "c": "107", "s": "0603", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "乙、測驗題部分", "subject": "社會工作管理", "year": "105", "exam_name": "105年第二次中醫師分階段營養師心理師護理師社工師暨法醫師語言治療師聽力師牙體技術師考試", "original_question_number": 19, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "socialworker", "db_exam_id": "social-worker"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('social-worker-moex-05929', 'social-worker', 'social-worker-moex-105-f2e04173', 'sub-social-worker-05', NULL, 'single_choice', '一個決策者過去曾準確地預測某事件發生之機率，造成相信「其實我早知道這件事會發生」的錯覺，因 而過度膨脹自己推估及決策之準確性，這種偏誤，叫做：', '["後見偏誤（hindsight bias）", "承諾遞升偏誤（escalation of commitment bias）", "定錨偏誤（anchoring bias）", "獨斷偏誤（arbitrary bias）"]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:10:32+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "9e4d5d193ead", "answer_pdf_sha1": "c3d41c596c6d", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "105090", "c": "107", "s": "0603", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "乙、測驗題部分", "subject": "社會工作管理", "year": "105", "exam_name": "105年第二次中醫師分階段營養師心理師護理師社工師暨法醫師語言治療師聽力師牙體技術師考試", "original_question_number": 20, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "socialworker", "db_exam_id": "social-worker"}'::jsonb, NULL)
